Overview
This project is a Hospital Management System designed to manage patient records, doctor details, appointments, and basic hospital operations efficiently.

Features
- Add, update, and delete patient records
- Manage doctor information
- Book and manage appointments
- Store medical history
- Simple and user-friendly interface

Technologies Used
- Programming Language: (e.g., Java / Python / C++)
- Database: (e.g., MySQL / SQLite / File Handling)
- Tools: (e.g., VS Code / IntelliJ / Eclipse)

Project Structure
- src/ → Source code files
- database/ → Database scripts or files
- docs/ → Documentation (if any)

How to Run
1. Clone or download the project
2. Open in your preferred IDE
3. Configure database (if required)
4. Run the main file

